Package com.virtudoc.web.entity

Class FileEntity

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.virtudoc.web.entity.FileEntity
  • @Entity
public class FileEntity
extends Object
    Database object that tracks user-generated files that are uploaded to the abstract storage layer. DO NOT create FileEntity objects directly. Instead use the FileService bean to generate a FileEntity after the data is successfully uploaded. Likewise, do not directly delete the FileEntity objects. This operation should be handled by the FileService as well.
    Author:
    ARMmaster17
    See Also:
    FileService
